      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "chn": "抱歉，我想得太入神了。",
      "jap": "すまぬ。考え耽っていた",
      "eng": "Forgive me. I was absorbed in thought.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "chn": "我是卡塔利纳的杰克麦雅。",
      "jap": "私はカタリナのジークマイヤー",
      "eng": "I am Siegmeyer of Catarina.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "chn": "老实说，我正有点困扰，",
      "jap": "実は、少し難儀しているのだ",
      "eng": "Quite honestly, I have run flat up against a wall.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "chn": "就是不知道怎么开这道门。",
      "jap": "そこの門が、どうしても開かなくてな",
      "eng": "Or, a gate, I should say. The thing just won't budge.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "chn": "我在这里一直等……就是没有办法打开，",
      "jap": "もうずっと待ってるのだが…どうにもならん",
      "eng": "No matter how long I wait. And, oh, have I waited!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "chn": "所以我才坐在这里思考要如何开门。",
      "jap": "だから、ここへ座って、思案している",
      "eng": "So, here I sit, in quite a pickle.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "chn": "真是烦恼啊！",
      "jap": "悩んでるんだよ！",
      "eng": "Weighing my options, so to speak!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
