      "index": 25,
      "chn": "老实说，我又有点困扰了。",
      "jap": "実は、また少し難儀しているのだ",
      "eng": "Yes, indeed, I have run up against a wall.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "chn": "……那边滚来滚去的铁球……",
      "jap": "…あの、鉄球ゴロゴロがな…",
      "eng": "...Or, a ball, to be precise.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "chn": "……你看，我胖胖的，对吧？\r\n铁球滚动的速度实在太快了……",
      "jap": "…ほら、私はなんとなく太っているだろう？\r\nゴロゴロが速すぎるんだ…",
      "eng": "...I'm afraid I'm a bit too plump\r\nto be outrunning those things.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "chn": "所以我才坐在这里思考解决方法。",
      "jap": "だから、ここへ座って、思案している",
      "eng": "So, here I sit, in quite a pickle.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "chn": "一定还有其他解决方法吧？",
      "jap": "また、なんとかなるかもしれないだろう？",
      "eng": "But who knows? Perhaps we'll have another development?",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "chn": "哈哈哈哈",
      "jap": "ガハハハハ",
